; Additional regression test for issue #2872
; Verify that a valid quoted commodity name with digits works correctly
; in a format directive (the unquoted case is diagnosed in 2872.test).
commodity "CTG25"
    format 1000.000 "CTG25"

2024/01/01 Quoted Valid
    Expenses        1000.000 "CTG25"
    Assets

test source -> 0
end test

test bal Expenses
      1000.000 CTG25  Expenses
end test
